HEADWORD: Cahincic
<hw>Ca*hin"cic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to, or
derived from, <etsep>cahinca</etsep>, the native name of a species of
Brazilian <gen>Chiococca</gen>, perhaps <spn>Chiococca racemosa</spn>;
<as>as, <ex>cahincic</ex> acid</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

